item.description:
@Pheega wrote:

[quote=“pk3r john, post:4, topic:281706”]A packet is not a case. Hell, they aren’t nearly the same thing.[/quote]The opcode packet is handled in the packetType switch statement. As far as the novice programmers are concerned, it is a case - because that’s where the rest of the packet data is read and handled.
